\newlabel{tab:cohort}{{3}{13}{Baseline characteristics and covariate definitions ($\mathbf {X}$) for the MIMIC-III analytic cohort within the 30-day observation window, stratified by outcome. \emph {Discharged} denotes patients censored alive before the window closes (the clinically informative censoring mechanism); \emph {Survived} denotes patients still alive at 30 days (administratively censored). Values are $n$ (\%) for categorical variables and mean $\pm $ SD or median [IQR] for continuous variables}{table.caption.7}{}}
